sequenceDiagram
	autonumber
	participant F as Farmer Client
	participant API as Express API
	participant FB as Firebase Auth
	participant M as MongoDB
	participant R as Redis
	participant WS as Socket.IO Server

	F->>API: POST /v1/listings (REST/JSON + Bearer token)
	API->>FB: verifyIdToken(token) (HTTPS/JWT)
	FB-->>API: uid, role=farmer
	API->>API: Validate body with Zod
	API->>M: insertOne(listing) (Mongo wire)
	M-->>API: insertedId
	API->>R: DEL kmb:listing:detail:{listingId}
	API->>R: PUBLISH kmb:pubsub:listings listing.created
	API->>WS: emit listing:created to crop-region room
	WS-->>F: WebSocket event ack
	API-->>F: 201 application/json {listingId}

